          <p style="font-family:Inter,sans-serif; font-weight:700; font-size:14px; color:#f5f0e8; margin:0;">Iodine</p>
          <span style="font-family:Inter,sans-serif; font-weight:700; font-size:13px; color:#C9A84C; white-space:nowrap; margin-left:12px;">150mcg</span>
        </div>
        <p style="font-family:Inter,sans-serif; font-size:12px; color:#666; line-height:1.6; margin:0;">Raw material the thyroid needs to produce T3 and T4 — most men are quietly deficient.</p>
      </div>

      <div style="background:#111111; border:1px solid #1e1e1e; padding:20px 22px;">
        <div style="display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:flex-start; margin-bottom:6px;">
