          <span style="font-family:Inter,sans-serif; font-weight:700; font-size:13px; color:#C9A84C; white-space:nowrap; margin-left:12px;">100mcg</span>
        </div>
        <p style="font-family:Inter,sans-serif; font-size:12px; color:#666; line-height:1.6; margin:0;">The conversion enzyme — converts inactive T4 into active T3. Without this, the whole chain stalls.</p>
