      <div style="background:#111111; border:1px solid #1e1e1e; padding:20px 22px;">
        <div style="display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:flex-start; margin-bottom:6px;">
          <p style="font-family:Inter,sans-serif; font-weight:700; font-size:14px; color:#f5f0e8; margin:0;">Zinc Picolinate</p>
          <span style="font-family:Inter,sans-serif; font-weight:700; font-size:13px; color:#C9A84C; white-space:nowrap; margin-left:12px;">30mg</span>
        </div>
        <p style="font-family:Inter,sans-serif; font-size:12px; color:#666; line-height:1.6; margin:0;">Activates thyroid receptors so T3 can actually bind and signal — 30mg Picolinate, not the 10mg powder most brands use.</p>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- COMPLEX LABEL — T SUPPORT -->
    <div style="margin-bottom:10px;">
      <div style="background:#0d1208; border:1px solid #2a3a20; border-radius:8px 8px 0 0; padding:10px 20px; display:inline-block;">
        <p style="font-family:Inter,sans-serif; font-weight:800; font-size:11px; letter-spacing:2px; text-transform:uppercase; color:#7ab87a; margin:0;">
          ⚡ T Support Complex
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap:2px; margin-bottom:24px;">

      <div style="background:#111111; border:1px solid #1e1e1e; padding:20px 22px;">
        <div style="display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:flex-start; margin-bottom:6px;">
          <p style="font-family:Inter,sans-serif; font-weight:700; font-size:14px; color:#f5f0e8; margin:0;">KSM-66 Ashwagandha</p>
          <span style="font-family:Inter,sans-serif; font-weight:700; font-size:13px; color:#C9A84C; white-space:nowrap; margin-left:12px;">600mg</span>
        </div>
        <p style="font-family:Inter,sans-serif; font-size:12px; color:#666; line-height:1.6; margin:0;">Lowers cortisol — the hormone that directly suppresses testosterone production. 600mg, the dose the clinical studies used.</p>
      </div>

      <div style="background:#111111; border:1px solid #1e1e1e; padding:20px 22px;">
        <div style="display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:flex-start; margin-bottom:6px;">
          <p style="font-family:Inter,sans-serif; font-weight:700; font-size:14px; color:#f5f0e8; margin:0;">Vitamin D3</p>
          <span style="font-family:Inter,sans-serif; font-weight:700; font-size:13px; color:#C9A84C; white-space:nowrap; margin-left:12px;">3,000 IU</span>
        </div>
        <p style="font-family:Inter,sans-serif; font-size:12px; color:#666; line-height:1.6; margin:0;">Acts as a steroid hormone precursor — men with low D3 consistently show lower testosterone across every major study.</p>
      </div>

      <div style="background:#111111; border:1px solid #1e1e1e; padding:20px 22px;">
        <div style="display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:flex-start; margin-bottom:6px;">
          <p style="font-family:Inter,sans-serif; font-weight:700; font-size:14px; color:#f5f0e8; margin:0;">Boron</p>
